00:12:53.101 --> 00:12:57.033
so I'll say negative
one to the n plus one,

00:12:57.033 --> 00:12:58.900
negative one to the n plus one power.

00:12:58.900 --> 00:12:59.833
Does that work?

00:12:59.833 --> 00:13:00.500
