00:13:04.766 --> 00:13:06.234
This is x to the third over one.

00:13:06.234 --> 00:13:07.802
When n is equal to two,

00:13:07.986 --> 00:13:10.966
this becomes negative,
which it needs to be,

00:13:10.966 --> 00:13:13.500
and then this becomes x to
the sixth, and we're over two,

00:13:13.500 --> 00:13:14.700
